{"tid":1533364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"速龍跑得好快, 手足, 特別女仔 要好小心","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T07:20:35.000Z","uid":156878,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7c86690534066bc7d828d365cecbbce55534e720","tid":1533364,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:02:10.000Z","msg":"頭先見個女仔被防暴追, 差廿/三十米就追到. <br />\n<br />\n粗略一計防暴跑100米大約15秒.<br />\n但通常200米就停.<br />\n<br />\n速龍會再快D.<br />\n而且追擊距離更長.<br />\n<br />\n加上我方後退時會有人或東西擋住, 同埋我方由發覺到轉身都要用1,2秒.<br />\n所以太近距離既話真係幾危險.<br />\n<br />\n所以自己試下跑100米要用幾耐, 全速200-300米又要幾耐同支唔支持到.<br />\n<br />\n再估計返安全距離."},{"pid":"4ec69d3ff715c90458b275315d11607dcae6b370","tid":1533364,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:51:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d03206b25160d3f96b71ad732abf3305727aa879","tid":1533364,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:53:38.000Z","msg":"有時會見到手足嘗試跨路中心「駁」位失敗被捕. 都要注意自己可唔可以越過個「駁」位"},{"pid":"11a93dfa70961a2e36f042c05fe606c806f40880","tid":1533364,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:58:39.000Z","msg":"［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ecfb311fdc67203e8276310f1b2a7bca801d0a","tid":1533364,"uid":38131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7c86690534066bc7d828d365cecbbce55534e720","tid":1533364,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:02:10.000Z","msg":"頭先見個女仔被防暴追, 差廿/三十米就追到. <br />\n<br />\n粗略一計防暴跑100米大約15秒.<br />\n但通常200米就停.<br />\n<br />\n速龍會再快D.<br />\n而且追擊距離更長.<br 